            <title>[SUREFIRE-418] Make an easier way to debug surefire booter temporary jar</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-418</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The surefire booter temporary jar can often be useful for manually reproducing Surefire failures.  When debugging is configured on the surefire plugin, we should configure the booter not to delete its temporary jar on exit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
